         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head>
            <p>Year 9: Epagathos <supplied reason="subaudible">son</supplied> of Heraklidas, three times an ephebe.</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>The normal duration of ephebic training seems to be 2 years, but there is evidence, e.g. from Chios, to suggest that it might last longer (PW s.v. 'Eφηβία col. 2744). The impression given here is that Epagathos was exceptional. <!-- but cf. 75, where it might --></p>
         </div>
         
